00:51:53,480 --> 00:52:00,130
♫ <i>No one but you could be her</i> ♫

665
00:52:00,130 --> 00:52:06,700
♫ <i>You were the first and only one</i> ♫

666
00:52:06,700 --> 00:52:11,720
♫ <i>Love was my greatest teacher</i> ♫

667
00:52:11,720 --> 00:52:15,130
♫ <i>I knew it then</i> ♫

668
00:52:18,190 --> 00:52:22,290
